--- !u!114 &1755491744
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1755491743}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 786a689c8741fef4f9c9fd55802d931b, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ImmersiveTutorialManager
  tutorialText: {fileID: 818103283}
  tutorialCanvasPanel: {fileID: 3881024}
  playButton: {fileID: 115895598}
  prevButton: {fileID: 1537303432}
  nextButton: {fileID: 359534678}
  passiDelTutorial:
  - spiegazione: "Press Play to activate the tutorial. \nPress the Settings icon
      to open the settings.\nPress the Home icon to start using SignVr \n\nYou'll
      be able to access the settings menu anytime you want during the tutorial."
    oggettiDaAttivare: []
  - spiegazione: Welcome to SignVR! In this tutorial you will learn how to use the
      app's interface. Let's start with the basics.
    oggettiDaAttivare: []
  - spiegazione: SignVR is a real-time translator for American Sign Language (ASL).
      This is Eliza, your virtual avatar. She will translate whatever you or the
      people nearby say.
    oggettiDaAttivare:
    - {fileID: 1728069902}
  - spiegazione: In this panel, a live transcription of the conversation will appear
      when people are talking.
    oggettiDaAttivare:
    - {fileID: 1880215249}
  - spiegazione: 'We also provide the Gloss notation transcription of the speech
      (written approximation of the American Sign Language)


      This way, you
      will learn and understand much faster!'
    oggettiDaAttivare:
    - {fileID: 1824760109}
  - spiegazione: Now, let's learn how to activate the microphone. Simply place your
      left hand towards you to make the microphone button appear. To activate it,
      press it with your right hand, just like a real button. When it turns green,
      it's ready to listen. Give it a try!
    oggettiDaAttivare:
    - {fileID: 97993188}
  - spiegazione: 'You can also use the controllers to set the microphone on by clicking
      the buttons A or X.

'
    oggettiDaAttivare:
    - {fileID: 1010337536}
    - {fileID: 1350680881}
    - {fileID: 89986561}
    - {fileID: 96212813}
  - spiegazione: When the microphone is listening, the text will turn green. After
      a few seconds, Eliza will translate everything the speaker says.
    oggettiDaAttivare: []
  - spiegazione: You can also adjust the position of the panels by pinching and grabbing
      them with your hands. Try it yourself!
    oggettiDaAttivare:
    - {fileID: 1728069902}
    - {fileID: 1880215249}
    - {fileID: 1824760109}
    - {fileID: 97993188}
  - spiegazione: To open the Settings menu, make a scissors gesture, with your wrist
      rotated slightly up.
    oggettiDaAttivare:
    - {fileID: 1128113309}
  - spiegazione: The settings menu is also accessible by pressing the B and Y buttons
      on the controllers.
    oggettiDaAttivare:
    - {fileID: 358963979}
    - {fileID: 721176385}
    - {fileID: 89986561}
    - {fileID: 96212813}
  - spiegazione: In the Settings, you can customize your experience. For example,
      you can disable the panels or change the avatar. You can also replay this tutorial
      from there.
    oggettiDaAttivare: []
  - spiegazione: "You are now ready to use SignVR!\nPress the Settings icon to access
      the settings. You can revise this tutorial there. \nIf you want to start the
      experience, press the home icon.\nSee you soon!"
    oggettiDaAttivare: []
